{"tid":1398808,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣做嘢】藍絲文宣策略再度進化","createTime":"2019-08-03T02:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:35:01.000Z","uid":118767,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b261f13bccab30ac94315765588e56ec0b43412a","tid":1398808,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/vPrYUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FvPrYUM.jpg&h=0f159e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/03/Cz1LT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F03%2FCz1LT6.jpg&h=8f295f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說今朝某個弱智親戚send咗呢兩幅圖嚟，一開始我冇為意，以為係普通曲圖，但睇真啲先發現背後用意之歹毒。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，正常嘅人對呢啲圖絕對可以免疫，但對一班蠢人、老人嚟講係另一回事，因為佢嘅誇張程度唔足以令（呢班）人一目了然，而且捏造嘅假資訊係建基喺部分事實之上，呢種程度嘅陰謀論亦滿足到佢地見解獨到嘅打飛機心態。<br />\n<br />\n其中一句「除了洗腦口罩，讓廢青吸入新鮮空氣，數秒鐘之內就會清醒」睇落可笑無害，但背後灌輸緊一種意識，就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">慫恿班弱智除義士嘅口罩！</span><br />\n<br />\n喺我平心靜氣同個親戚解釋完一輪後，佢竟然同我講寧可信其有，小心駛得萬年船。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而特別之處係我呢位親戚並唔係傳統藍絲，佢只係一個今時今日仲我講要用打坐、誦經救香港嘅天線得得B。你話我諗多咗又好咩都好，呢兩張圖嘅出現已經唔係為咗俾藍絲圍爐取暖咁簡單，佢執住毒品呢個point無限放大，係利用咗一般長輩對年青人嘅關愛從內進行分裂、離間，其殺傷性不可忽視。<br />\n<br />\n建議文宣反擊方法：<br />\n<br />\n要改就改得比佢更誇張，例如話戴咗有毒口罩三日內會感染T病毒變喪屍，專門攻擊所有藍絲親戚，務求令一班蠢親戚知道當初取信幅圖係幾咁弱智。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3e5b427839f173d1e1326c0e2c4b481f0b7c2c","tid":1398808,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"838146d5af40d7ecb200e16b04bba9498a120868","tid":1398808,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"自己親戚自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16a4b43566126778224bf4f80902317142d9075","tid":1398808,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6dce218f435f1905d901398508f31697997a30","tid":1398808,"uid":272837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"睇到笑咗岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推！！！"},{"pid":"a1b177c67224ac76a4b80821c69dff345590e3e4","tid":1398808,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d10231cd523865c850237c853268645615bda4ca","tid":1398808,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:11:04.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5784656b09b61f2afeeea906781b9bde177227bc","tid":1398808,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:16:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e533395e7815d2528ce20e6f66dec04e8ad53e71","tid":1398808,"uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"弱智到咁 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e18b09b79d88da6b719c3408db910d3ce2821","tid":1398808,"uid":8833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFJxfnh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFJxfnh.png&h=ee294784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3160fdb5c12cf91729258cb0655a743fa40b656","tid":1398808,"uid":264911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:18:42.000Z","m